content:
Create a Basic Chat Implementation

Before customizing Chat, create the basic Chat implementation for your Salesforce org. This will give you a functioning Chat implementation that agents can use to chat with customers.

Available in: 
- Salesforce Classic
- Performance Editions and Developer Edition orgs created after June 14, 2012
- Unlimited Edition and Enterprise Edition with Service Cloud

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED:
- Customize Application (to set up Chat)
- Manage Profiles and Permission Sets (to create user profiles and permission sets)

IMPORTANT: 
The legacy chat product is scheduled for retirement on February 14, 2026. Migrate to Messaging for In-App and Web before that date.

Create Chat Users
